---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout>
  <main class="prose">
    <h1>I build software for people and small businesses</h1>

    <p>
      I'm a software engineer based in Cape Town with experience building
      web applications from the ground up — from idea to production. Whether
      you need an MVP to validate a product, a custom internal tool to streamline
      your workflow, or a full-featured web app, I can help.
    </p>

    <h2>What I can build for you</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Web applications and MVPs</li>
      <li>Internal tools and dashboards</li>
      <li>APIs and backend services</li>
      <li>Automations that save your team time</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How I work</h2>
    <p>
      I keep things simple and pragmatic. I'll work with you to understand the
      problem, build what you actually need, and ship it. No bloat, no
      unnecessary complexity — just software that works.
    </p>

    <h2>Get in touch</h2>
    <p>
      Reach out on <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/john-prutton/"
        target="_blank">LinkedIn</a
      > and let's talk about what you're building.
    </p>
  </main>
</Layout>
